Package: pallet
Title: Directory-level Imports for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Tymoteusz", "Makowski", email = "tymek.makowski@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: pallet brings directory-level imports to R. It allows importing
    an entire directory as a whole without exposing every function in it.
